title: How Much is Your Knowledge Worth?
itunes:title: How Much is Your Knowledge Worth?
description:
You know the information you have in your brain, how much do you think all of that is worth? If you were to charge someone to learn that information from you, how much would you charge them? I promise you this, it is worth more than you know! This is what we will be talking about today!

Join my Free 4 Day Attract & Convert Workshop for Coaches here: https://www.thecoachworkshop.com/
